    <item>
      <title>特朗普对封口费判决提出上诉，开启新一轮法律战</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-appeals-hush-money-verdict-kicking-off-fresh-legal-fight</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普总统对纽约封口费案的有罪判决正式提起上诉，引发了一场新的法律战。在特朗普就职前几天，美国最高法院拒绝撤销对他的定罪判决，这场法律战不可避免地随之而来。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-appeals-hush-money-verdict-kicking-off-fresh-legal-fight</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:17:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普撤销引发混乱的支出冻结令</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-reverses-spending-freeze-order-that-sparked-chaos</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普撤销了冻结一系列联邦拨款、贷款和财政援助的命令，这是在政府和非营利组织经历数日的不确定性和焦虑之后出现的戏剧性逆转。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/white-house-reverses-spending-freeze-order-that-sparked-chaos</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:12:20 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普官员讨论对英伟达中国销售实施更严格的限制</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-officials-discuss-tightening-curbs-on-nvidia-china-sales</link>
      <description><![CDATA[知情人士透露，特朗普政府官员正在探索对英伟达公司向中国出售芯片采取更多限制措施。他们强调，谈判还处于非常早期的阶段，新团队正在研究政策优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/trump-officials-discuss-tightening-curbs-on-nvidia-china-sales</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:01:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>里夫斯的希思罗机场助推增长计划将需要数年时间才能实现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/rachel-reeves-heathrow-fueled-growth-plan-will-take-years-to-get-off-ground</link>
      <description><![CDATA[雷切尔·里夫斯 (Rachel Reeves) 努力通过风力涡轮机、道路、机场、铁路、贸易协议以及养老金、规划和福利制度改革来重振英国低迷的经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-29/rachel-reeves-heathrow-fueled-growth-plan-will-take-years-to-get-off-ground</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 29 Jan 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
